debrief.itemText: Please answer the following questions about your experience. Click and drag the red scrollbar to move down. Do not leave any box blank. Type ‘no’ or ‘n/a’ if you don’t have a response.
Briefly describe what you were asked to do in this experiment? (if there is existing text in the box delete it.
debrief.response: I was shown letters and numbers and then asked to press cooresponding keys. When shown a letter I had to press "d" if the letter was closer to A and press "F" if  the letter was closer to Z. If there was a number shown i had to press "J" if the number was less than 53 and press "K" if the number was above 53.

debrief.itemText: Was there any part of the experiment that you found to be confusing?
Please explain anything you found confusing. (if No, type ‘No’)
debrief.response: When going through the expirement it was hard for me to find if there was nay pattern. As well, i found it hard to press the keys within the time limit.
